00:50:16.480 --> 00:50:19.120
So the key thing
in OPM is there's

00:50:19.120 --> 00:50:21.550
only one type of diagram.

00:50:21.550 --> 00:50:23.290
And there's also
natural language

00:50:23.290 --> 00:50:24.820
