NAREK SHOUGARIAN: Thank you.

01:31:16.220 --> 01:31:16.980
So hello, everyone.

01:31:16.980 --> 01:31:17.688
My name is Narek.

01:31:17.688 --> 01:31:20.720
I'm a doctoral student
